text: Salih Hassan (born 26 December 1962) is a British rower. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics, 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:British male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Greater London
